  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-ON-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "Synthetic adversarial package derived from the Morrison COU2 VAD hemolysis credibility assessment. The ContextOfUse is fully described in prose and references operating ranges (5 flow-speed combinations, Class III VAD), but omits both hasApplicabilityConstraint and hasOperatingEnvelope structured links, leaving the model's valid operating envelope formally unspecified. This triggers W-ON-02 (unbounded applicability). All 13 credibility factors are populated; the overall decision is Accepted to ensure the weakness is not masked by an outright rejection.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/cou2-vad-hemolysis-req",
